    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Meta label -->
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2 rounded-full border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-500/10 mb-10">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-amber-400 animate-pulse"></span>
            <span class="section-num text-amber-400">Video Notes · 2026</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-7xl md:text-8xl font-extrabold leading-tight mb-8 tracking-tight">
            <span class="gradient-amber">AI 如何重新定義</span><br>
            <span class="text-white">軟體開發</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-gray-400 mb-5 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            Martin Fowler × Kent Beck 深度對談筆記
        </p>

        <p class="text-base text-gray-500 mb-12">
            兩位軟體工藝大師從歷史、工藝、社會、職涯四個視角，拆解 AI 浪潮對軟體開發的深遠影響
        </p>

